OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain mostly cloudy this evening and
OL,7,Ftonight with frequent showers, some
OL,8,Fheavy, and a few drier clearer
OL,9,Fintervals. Freshening northwesterly
OL,10,Fwinds by morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FRather cloudy with rain or
OL,13,Fshowers, some turning heavy at times.
OL,14,FModerate to fresh west to northwest
OL,15,Fbreeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
